One of the hardest things about 2023 was losing my little cloud baby. We lost her in August, and I haven’t been able to talk about it because I wasn’t really ready to accept it. 
RIP Princess Leia, my little fluffer angel. I miss you every day and I am so grateful that I got to be your family for 13 lucky years. 🌈💕🐩💕🌈
